SELECT
	usercode,
	date_format( attdate, '%Y-%m-01' ) AS yyyymm,
	date_format( attdate, '%d' ) AS dd,
	onduty_type,
	offduty_type 
FROM
	attendance_daily a 
WHERE
	attdate >= date_sub( date_sub(CURRENT_DATE, INTERVAL extract( DAY FROM CURRENT_DATE )- 1 DAY ), INTERVAL 1 MONTH )
